One could theoretically calculate what is required for an elephant to hang from the side of a cliff with it's tail tied to a daisy.<br>
<br>
One would be very hard pressed to <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> PROVE</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> this. For this to be proven by physics you would need a working model.<br>
