I understand the point you were trying to make btw, but Physics is tied to the real world and its observations, its not based on false assumptions or invalid results. Mathematics is often used to describe the different sciences and as such is also tied to real life models.<br>
<br>
If we were to know all of the functions and equations that EQ uses to calculate hits then we could predict possibilites and their probabilities. It is, after all, generated on a COMPUTER which is based on mathematical algorithims.<br>
